latestPosts.caption:
You’ve seen the products. Now meet the face behind it all 💜

It started with one person — overwhelmed by the chaos of skincare. Too many steps. Too much noise. Too little joy.

Meet @ishika__arora_ — the mind, the heart, and let’s be real, a bit of the beautiful chaos behind GAGA 💫

What began as frustration with skincare that felt like homework turned into a bold, playful, no-BS brand — one that’s joyful, intentional, and made for real people with everyday skin🥰

This video is a little peek into how it all began. And let’s just say… the best is yet to come 🤌🏻

Star-shaped, heart-shaped pimple patches do look cute — but are they really doing the job? That’s the question we kept coming back to while working on Touch Me Not 😌

We discovered that hydrocolloid works BEST in its purest form, so we skipped the cute and went for pimple patches that are invisibly thin, matte, and have ingredients that actually work while you sleep 💤 

So no, our patches may not win design awards.
But they will win against breakouts. And honestly, that’s the only win that matters 💖
